 Galvatron flew out of the base. He had senced an old foe. He needed to 
finish what he started. Now 3 times as powerful as before he would crush this 
bot easily. He landed infront of the bot. The bots position was only about 50 
feet from the base so it was quite easily reached in ashort amount of time. 
He landed infront  of the good bot. "Ready to meet Primus?"
